00:00:29.450 --> 00:00:33.770 align:middle line:84%
has confirmed water in sunlit
areas of the lunar surface.

00:00:33.770 --> 00:00:37.100 align:middle line:10%
H2O molecules were detected
in the Clavius crater

00:00:37.100 --> 00:00:39.140 align:middle line:10%
on the moon's
southern hemisphere.

00:00:39.140 --> 00:00:42.680 align:middle line:84%
